Congratulations. You have, for whatever reason, been granted the distinction of being one of the very few in history to find the hidden section of the Hogwarts Library. That means that, for whatever reason, the consciousness of the Library has deemed you to be “interesting”. There are a few things that you should know, before you venture too much further into the its depths.